-- Noir --

Noir's optics focus on Gatara, and she nods her aknowledgement at 
the bot. The rather large Rogue named Gatara was known to her, and 
her memories to be a formidal ally, and not one to be trifled with.

"Some living, some are already dead." She pauses, the continues 
before Gatara can say anything, "Where is Devilcat, and what is the 
Rogues current situation on wherever it is we have landed. 
Unfortunately my memory has a few blanks still, and I can not 
remember our final destination."
